  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may improve a target&#8217;s ability to work alone. The target can use the aid another action to aid themselves as a swift action. The bonus they gain from doing so is equal to +3 instead of +2, and increases by +1 for every 5 caster levels. In any round they do so, they may not benefit from another creature aiding them.</p>\n<p>The target may discharge this effect to treat all enemies as flanked as long as none of the target&#8217;s allies threaten the enemy. This effect lasts one round per caster level.</p>\n",
